It's a piece of conversation that's fully deciphered online at The Nation.
For your fans from Costa Rica, it's a dream that Pearl Jam will play in Costa Rica.
A trip to Costa Rica is a dream come true for us too.
It's just our second visit to South and Central America, and so far it's going well.
I've only been to Costa Rica once on vacation, it's a beautiful country, and I think we can stay there for a few days.
