The leadership of a large coalition of social-democrats and Christian Democrats in power in Austria decided on Tuesday to write the budget “gold rule” into the Constitution to reduce the budget deficit and thus avoid possible decline by the rating agencies of Austria ' s state credit rating (trip A).
